text: The 2020 United States presidential election in Wyoming was held on Tuesday 3rd November, 2020 in Wyoming as part of the 2020 United States presidential election. Donald Trump and his running mate for Vice President, Mike Pence had won 3 electoral votes in the Electoral College. == References == Category:2020 United States presidential election Category:21st century in Wyoming
title: 2020 United States presidential election in Wyoming
